## Dependencies & sequencing
```
M20.0 (license/accounts, ⛔) ─┬─> M20.1 (bundle mcp server) ──> M20.2 (npm publish) ─┬─> M20.4 (Claude plugin)
                             │                                                      ├─> M20.5 (client configs/docs)
                             └───────────────────────────> M20.3 (Marketplace/OpenVSX; .vsix already self-contained)
M20.2 + M20.3 + M20.4 + M20.5 ──> M20.6 (interop + release, ⛔)
M20.7 optional, after M20.3
```
Critical path: **M20.0 → M20.1 → M20.2 → {M20.4, M20.5} → M20.6**. M20.3 parallels once M20.0 clears.

