## Verification (end-to-end, when executed)
1. **Clean-machine gate** (extends M19.4 to the MCP server): no repo checkout — `npm i -g @iap/cli && iap validate`; `npx @iap/mcp-server` handshake.
2. **Marketplace gate:** install from Marketplace (VS Code) and OpenVSX (Cursor); open `infrastructure.iap.yaml`; confirm live diagnostics. (Offline `extensions/vscode/smoke.mjs` already proves the self-contained LSP round-trip pre-publish.)
3. **Claude plugin gate:** `claude plugin install iap`; call `iap_author` then `iap_validate` in a session.
4. **Interop matrix:** each of the 5 clients lists the 5 tools and runs one author + one analysis call.
5. **Regression:** `pnpm run verify` green (with new `smoke:mcp`); existing `smoke:vsix` still green; `check:names` green; no deploy/mutation tool exposed to any client.
